What we are adding is:

bundle-items/
├── files.yml
├── collections-hub.yml
├── rhel8iso.yml
├── rhel9iso.yml
├── bootstrap.yml
└── third-party-rhel8-rpms.yml

Then in .gitlab-ci.yml, you can call them like this:

bundle_item_ids: |
  files
  collections-hub
  rhel8iso
  third-party-rhel8-rpms
  bootstrap

That means you do not have to repeat the full item definition in every profile.

